---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../components/Breadcrumb.astro';

const lastUpdated = '19 February 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy â€” DURIAN"
  description="How DURIAN handles your data. GDPR-compliant. We never sell your information."
  breadcrumb={[{ name: 'Privacy Policy', url: 'https://duriantravel.com/privacy-policy/' }]}
  noindex={true}
>
  <div class="container">
    <Breadcrumb items={[{ name: 'Privacy Policy' }]} />
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <header class="legal-header">
        <h1 class="legal-header__title">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="legal-header__meta">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </header>

      <div class="prose">
        <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
        <p>
          DURIAN ("we", "us", "our") is a visa application strategy consultancy
          providing educational guidance. For data protection purposes, we are the data controller
          of your personal information collected through this website.
        </p>

        <h2>2. What Data We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect the following personal data when you use our website or services:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Contact information:</strong> name, email address</li>
          <li><strong>Application information:</strong> nationality, visa type, general situation (only what you voluntarily provide)</li>
          <li><strong>Communication records:</strong> your messages and our responses</li>
          <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> pages visited (via privacy-respecting analytics, if applicable)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We do not collect sensitive visa application data such as passport numbers, financial account
          details, or visa refusal letters unless explicitly shared by you in session communications.
        </p>

        <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <p>We use your personal data only for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Responding to your enquiries and booking requests</li>
          <li>Delivering the service you engaged us for</li>
          <li>Communicating about your consultation or audit</li>
          <li>Sending relevant content updates (only with your consent)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Legal Basis</h2>
        <p>We process your data on the following legal bases:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Contract performance:</strong> to deliver services you've requested</li>
          <li><strong>Legitimate interests:</strong> to respond to enquiries and improve our services</li>
          <li><strong>Consent:</strong> for any marketing communications (you can withdraw at any time)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.
          We may share data with service providers (e.g., form hosting, email providers) under strict
          data processing agreements, only as necessary to deliver our service.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain your data for as long as necessary to deliver the service and for a reasonable period
          thereafter. Contact form submissions are retained for up to 2 years. You may request deletion
          at any time.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under applicable data protection law (including GDPR), you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Object to or restrict processing of your data</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
          <li>Lodge a complaint with your supervisory authority</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise your rights, please <a href="/contact/" class="link">contact us</a>.</p>

        <h2>8. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          This website uses no third-party advertising cookies. We may use technically necessary
          cookies for form functionality. We do not track visitors for advertising purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this policy periodically. We will notify you of significant changes by
          updating the "last updated" date at the top.
        </p>

        <h2>10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For any privacy-related questions, please <a href="/contact/" class="link">contact us</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.legal-header { margin-bottom: var(--space-10); }
.legal-header__title { font-size: clamp(var(--text-3xl), 4vw, var(--text-4xl)); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
.legal-header__meta  { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm); }
</style>
